welcome.name: General
welcome.content:
# Introduction
Memer API is a powerful API that allows you to manipulate images very easily.


# How to get premium?
1) Go to this [Link](https://ko-fi.com/memerapi)

2) Subscribe to a monthly package

3) Join our discord server 

4) Type "meme getpremium" in any channel to get your token

5) Premium users shall make the request to [Premium Special API](https://premium.memer-api.live), which has no limits

# What is an Authentication token?
You need an auth token to use the API, which can be obtained from our [Discord server](https://discord.com/invite/emD44ZJaSA).

# Is there any Rate-limit?
Free Users can request once every 6 seconds to each endpoint

# Need Help?
Join our discord server to get help - [Discord](https://discord.com/invite/emD44ZJaSA)

# Javascript Package
Javascript users can use our js package from [Memer JS](https://memer-api.js.org)        
We have a premium package for js users as well(included with API premium)
